  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced rest meat and cook until browned.",
    "Add the diced bitter melon and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the sweetcorn kernels and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked rice to the skillet or wok and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the soy sauce, salt, and black pepper, and stir-fry for another minute.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
